# .tdd-ignore — ERE patterns; lines matching any are dropped from stub-scan results.
# This is a Next.js documentation site. Code examples shown to readers
# legitimately contain console.log / debugger / etc. as illustrative output.
# Real source code lives outside the docs/ tree and is still scanned normally.

console\.log\(            # console.log inside code-sample template literals (docs)
console\.debug\(          # same
console\.error\(          # same
console\.warn\(           # same
debugger;?                # example debugging step
